text: Connie Sellecca (born Concetta Sellecchia on May 25, 1955 in Bronx, New York) is an American actress and former model who has starred in many television programs and many movies. She was nominated for a Golden Globe Award for Best Actress in a Television Series Drama in 1987. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:American bloggers Category:Actors from New York (state) Category:American Christians Category:American YouTubers Category:American movie actors Category:American models Category:People from the Bronx Category:Pseudonyms Category:Television producers
